co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib

Class PartitionFilter.Condition<T extends Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib.PartitionFilter.Condition<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the partitioning field.
    Enclosing class:
    PartitionFilter

    public static class PartitionFilter.Condition<T extends Comparable<T>>
extends Object
    Represents a condition on a partitioning field, by means of an inclusive lower bound and an exclusive upper bound. As a special case, if only one value is passed to the constructor, then this represents an equality filter.
